item.title: Need a compiler for pimpscape
item.dc:creator: @tor0en tor0en
item.description:
@tor0en wrote:

all compliers fit to all sources xD well its easy to make one
add this:

echo off@
color 03
title Complier
“javac” *.java
pause
exit

where it says javac, u need to put in the link to the javac.exe file. the javac file will be in the java folder in the folder of the jdk u got and then a folder named bin. so my link would be:
C:\ProgramFiler\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe

so find urs and put that in, and remember use \ , not /
